dc:description: Brown. Good condition. Smooth tapering square handle decorated with four concentric dotted circles, one on each side, each with dark paint. Notched at top below projecting ridge. Ridge incised once on one side, twice on other. Clappers decorated with incised parallel lines and three concentric dotted circles, each identical to handle circles.
